#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:2
msgid "自动编程"
msgstr "Auto-Programming"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:4
msgid "本节说明两种自动编程模式，以及上传 CAD/元件信息文件后的字段映射与坐标对齐流程。"
msgstr ""
"This section covers the two Auto-Programming modes, plus field mapping "
"and coordinate alignment after uploading a CAD / component-info file."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:7
msgid ""
"向导的前三步（基本信息、上板与拍摄、配置自动编程）在 :ref:`创建产品` 中已有详细说明。 本页聚焦于向导第四步\"添加CAD "
"(可选)\"：上传 CAD 并运行自动编程。"
msgstr ""
"The first three wizard steps (Basic Info, Conveyor & Capture, Configure "
"Auto-Program) are documented in :ref:`创建产品`. This page focuses on the "
"fourth step, \"Add CAD (Optional)\": uploading CAD and running auto-"
"programming."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:10
msgid "**两种编程模式对比**"
msgstr "**Comparison of the two programming modes**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:12
msgid "**全自动编程（无 CAD）** — 完全依赖视觉 + AI 自动识别、分割与建模所有器件，生成初始检测框。"
msgstr ""
"**Full Auto-Programming (no CAD)** — relies entirely on vision + AI to "
"detect, segment, and model every component and generate the initial "
"inspection boxes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:13
msgid ""
"**半自动编程（上传 CAD）** — 在视觉预测结果的基础上，将 CAD 行记录与模型识别的元件自动匹配，直接赋值标识 "
"(Designator)、封装 (Package)、料号 (PN)，并支持按封装/料号分组。"
msgstr ""
"**Semi-Auto Programming (with CAD)** — on top of the vision results, "
"automatically matches CAD rows to detected components, fills in "
"designator / package / part number, and supports grouping by package or "
"PN."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:15
msgid ""
"上传 CAD 不影响自动编程的速度与基础质量；它提供\"结构化属性 + 分组\"增益， "
"使数据集在后续训练/反馈阶段更快积累\"同类多样本\"，更容易较早获得稳定效果。"
msgstr ""
"Uploading CAD does not affect Auto-Programming speed or baseline quality;"
" it adds *structured attributes + grouping*, letting the dataset "
"accumulate same-class samples faster during later training / feedback, so"
" stable performance is reached sooner."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:18
msgid "无 CAD 情况下仍可在后续通过手动补录和检测反馈机制逐渐丰富数据集。"
msgstr ""
"Without CAD, the dataset can still be enriched gradually through manual "
"entry and inspection feedback later on."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:20
msgid "**第四步：添加CAD (可选)**"
msgstr "**Step 4: Add CAD (Optional)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:22
msgid "完成 **配置自动编程** 步骤后，向导进入第四步 **添加CAD (可选)**。此步骤有三个选项："
msgstr ""
"Once the **Configure Auto-Program** step is complete, the wizard advances"
" to Step 4, **Add CAD (Optional)**. The step offers three actions:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:24
msgid "**返回全景采集** — 返回上一步重新拍摄。"
msgstr "**Back to Full Capture** — return to the previous step to re-shoot."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:25
msgid "**手动编程** — 跳过自动编程，直接进入产品编程界面。"
msgstr ""
"**Manual Programming** — skip Auto-Programming and go straight to the "
"product programming page."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:26
msgid "**运行自动编程** — 在未上传 CAD 文件时，点击此按钮执行全自动编程。"
msgstr ""
"**Run Auto-Programming** — with no CAD uploaded, this button runs Full "
"Auto-Programming."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:28
msgid "若已上传 CAD 文件，则显示 **运行自动编程** 按钮，点击后执行半自动编程。"
msgstr ""
"Once a CAD file is uploaded, the same **Run Auto-Programming** button "
"runs Semi-Auto Programming."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:30
msgid "检测区域已在上一步 **配置自动编程** 中定义，本步骤无需再次框选（见 :ref:`创建产品`）。"
msgstr ""
"The inspection region was already defined on the previous **Configure "
"Auto-Program** step, so there is no need to box it again here (see "
":ref:`创建产品`)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:32
msgid ""
"**运行自动编程** 按钮旁还有 **自动训练** 复选框；它与编程完成后的拼板构建、模型训练自动化详见下文 "
"**编程后的自动处理：拼板构建与模型训练**。"
msgstr ""
"Next to the **Run auto programming** button there is also an **Auto-train"
" after programming** checkbox; for what it does — together with the panel"
" building and model training that run automatically after programming — "
"see **Post-programming automation: panel building and model training** "
"below."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:34
msgid "**全自动编程（无 CAD）**"
msgstr "**Full Auto-Programming (no CAD)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:36
msgid "未上传任何文件时，点击 **运行自动编程** 即可开始纯视觉检测编程："
msgstr ""
"With no file uploaded, click **Run Auto-Programming** to start vision-"
"only programming:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "上传 CAD 文件界面（未上传时点击运行自动编程）"
msgstr "Upload-CAD screen (click *Run Auto-Programming* with no file uploaded)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:42
msgid "系统会基于 **配置自动编程** 步骤中定义的自动编程检测类型，自动识别并分割所选类别器件，生成初始的检测框。"
msgstr ""
"The system uses the auto-programming inspection types defined on the "
"**Configure Auto-Program** step to detect and segment matching "
"components, then generates the initial inspection boxes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:44
msgid "自动编程约需 30 秒完成。是否提供 CAD 文件不影响编程质量。"
msgstr ""
"Auto-Programming takes about 30 seconds. Providing a CAD file does not "
"affect the programming quality."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "全自动编程示意"
msgstr "Full Auto-Programming illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:50
msgid "完成后会进入产品编程界面，从这一步开始，需要定义对齐标记、确认检测框、微调参数，详见后续章节。"
msgstr ""
"When it finishes, the wizard hands off to the product programming page; "
"from there you define alignment marks, verify inspection boxes, and tune "
"parameters. Those steps are covered in the following chapters."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:52
msgid "**半自动编程（上传 CAD）**"
msgstr "**Semi-Auto Programming (with CAD)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:54
msgid "**支持的文件格式**"
msgstr "**Supported file formats**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:56
msgid "支持导入 SMT 机台导出的标准元件信息文件（`.csv`、`.tsv`、`.txt`）。文件须为 UTF-8 编码。"
msgstr ""
"Standard component-info files exported by SMT machines are supported "
"(`.csv`, `.tsv`, `.txt`). The file must be UTF-8 encoded."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:58
msgid "可以包含以下字段："
msgstr "The file may contain the following fields:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:60
msgid "（可选）料号 (PN)"
msgstr "(Optional) Part Number (PN)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:61
msgid "封装号 (Package)"
msgstr "Package"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:62
msgid "标识 (Designator / Ref)"
msgstr "Designator / Ref"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:63
msgid "中心X坐标 (Center X)、中心Y坐标 (Center Y)"
msgstr "Center X, Center Y"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:64
msgid "旋转角度 (Rotation °)"
msgstr "Rotation (°)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:65
msgid "（可选）层 / 面别字段（如 TOP/BOTTOM）"
msgstr "(Optional) Layer / side field (e.g. TOP / BOTTOM)"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:67
msgid "导入 CAD 的好处："
msgstr "Benefits of importing CAD:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:69
msgid "自动匹配并写入标识 / 封装 / 料号，避免后期逐个补录。"
msgstr ""
"Auto-matches and writes Designator / Package / Part Number — no per-"
"component entry later."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:70
msgid "按封装 / 料号即时分组，初始数据集中\"同一类\"样本数量有效放大。"
msgstr ""
"Immediate package / part-number grouping multiplies the same-class sample"
" count in the initial dataset."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:71
msgid "更早形成可复用的封装级统计（缺陷、尺寸、阈值分布），降低后续参数微调成本。"
msgstr ""
"Reusable package-level statistics (defect, size, threshold distributions)"
" form sooner, reducing later parameter-tuning effort."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:72
msgid "协助发现坐标 / 单位 / 重复记录等 CAD 异常。"
msgstr ""
"Helps surface CAD anomalies — bad coordinates, wrong units, duplicate "
"rows."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:74
msgid "**操作步骤**"
msgstr "**Steps**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:76
msgid "**步骤一：导入元件信息文件**"
msgstr "**Step 1: Import the component-info file**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:78
msgid "在 **添加CAD (可选)** 步骤中，点击 **选择文件** 上传一个 `.csv`（或 `.tsv`、`.txt`）文件。"
msgstr ""
"On the **Add CAD (Optional)** step, click **Select File** to upload a "
"`.csv` (or `.tsv` / `.txt`) file."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "导入元件信息文件界面"
msgstr "Component-info file import screen"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:84
msgid "**步骤二：解析文件与字段映射**"
msgstr "**Step 2: Parse the file and map fields**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:86
msgid "文件上传成功后，进入 **解析文件** 界面。左侧显示文件原始内容，右侧为解析与字段映射面板。"
msgstr ""
"Once uploaded, the wizard advances to the **Parse File** screen. The raw "
"file is shown on the left; parsing and field mapping happen on the right."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:88
msgid "**第一行索引 / 最后一行索引** — 指定 CSV 数据的起始行号和结束行号（从 1 计数）。"
msgstr ""
"**First Row Index / Last Row Index** — the start and end row numbers of "
"the CSV data (1-based)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:89
msgid "**忽略底层** — 若仅检测正面（顶层），开启此开关后须填写底层标识符（如 `B`、`BOT`），系统会自动过滤底层行。"
msgstr ""
"**Ignore Bottom Side** — when inspecting only the top side, enable the "
"switch and supply the bottom-side identifier (such as `B` or `BOT`) so "
"the system filters out bottom-side rows."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:90
msgid "点击 **预览表格** — 系统按当前设置解析并显示表格内容，每列顶部显示一个下拉菜单。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Preview Table** — the system parses the file with the current "
"settings and displays the table; each column header shows a drop-down."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:92
msgid "**字段映射（映射数据）**"
msgstr "**Field mapping (Map Data)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:94
msgid "在 **映射数据** 区域，为每一列在下拉菜单中指定对应的字段类型："
msgstr ""
"In the **Map Data** area, assign each column to its field type via the "
"drop-down:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:96
msgid "**封装号** — 对应 CAD 中的封装名称（Package）。"
msgstr "**Package** — maps to the CAD package name."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:97
msgid "**料号** — 对应 CAD 中的料号（Part No.，可选）。"
msgstr "**Part Number** — maps to the CAD part number (optional)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:98
msgid "**中心X坐标** / **中心Y坐标** — X/Y 坐标列（必选）。"
msgstr "**Center X / Center Y** — the X / Y coordinate columns (required)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:99
msgid "**旋转角度** — 元件旋转角度列。"
msgstr "**Rotation** — the component rotation angle column."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:100
msgid "**层** — 面别标识列（如已启用忽略底层，需指定此列）。"
msgstr ""
"**Layer** — the side-identifier column (required if *Ignore Bottom Side* "
"is on)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:101
msgid "**丝印/位号/标识** — 元件位号（Ref Designator）列（必选）。"
msgstr "**Designator** — the reference designator column (required)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:102
msgid "**忽略此列** — 对不需要的列选择此项。"
msgstr "**Ignore this column** — for columns you don't need."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "CAD 字段映射示意"
msgstr "CAD field mapping illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:108
msgid "**坐标单位** — 在\"坐标单位\"下拉菜单中选择 **毫米** 或 **密尔** (mil)，须与 CAD 文件一致。"
msgstr ""
"**Coordinate Unit** — choose **mm** or **mil** in the *Coordinate Unit* "
"drop-down; it must match the CAD file."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:111
msgid "若运行后提示坐标偏差过大，首先检查坐标单位（mil ↔ mm）是否选择正确。"
msgstr ""
"If the run reports a large coordinate deviation, first check that the "
"coordinate unit (mil ↔ mm) is correct."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:113
msgid ""
"**使用元件模板**（可选）— 勾选 **使用元件模板** 后，系统会对匹配到已保存元件模板的 CAD 点使用模板定义的区域替代 AI "
"检测结果。需 CAD 坐标先对齐方可生效。"
msgstr ""
"**Use Component Templates** (optional) — when checked, CAD entries that "
"match a saved component template use the template's region instead of the"
" AI-detected region. Effective only after the CAD coordinates are "
"aligned."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:115
msgid "**仅编程 CAD 中的元件** — 可选。勾选后，AI 检测到但 CAD 文件中不存在的元件将被丢弃，仅保留与 CAD 匹配的元件。默认不勾选。"
msgstr ""
"**Only program components in CAD** — optional. When checked, components "
"detected by AI that are not present in the CAD file are discarded, "
"keeping only those matched to the CAD. Unchecked by default."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:117
msgid ""
"**CAD 对齐容差 (px)** — 可选。投影后的 CAD "
"点与检测到的元件之间允许的最大像素距离，超过则在对齐时不视为匹配；数值越大越宽松，越小越严格。默认 30，设为 0 将完全无法匹配。"
msgstr ""
"**CAD alignment tolerance (px)** — optional. The maximum pixel distance "
"between a projected CAD point and a detected component for them to count "
"as matched during alignment; larger values are more lenient, smaller "
"values are stricter. Default 30; 0 disables matching entirely."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:119
msgid ""
"上述 **使用元件模板**、**仅编程 CAD 中的元件** 与 **CAD 对齐容差 (px)** 选项在 **解析文件** 与 "
"**对齐坐标** 界面（重新分析时）均可设置。"
msgstr ""
"The **Use Component Templates**, **Only program components in CAD**, and "
"**CAD alignment tolerance (px)** options can all be set on both the "
"**Parse File** and **Align Coordinates** screens (the latter when re-"
"analyzing)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:121
msgid "**步骤三：运行半自动编程**"
msgstr "**Step 3: Run Semi-Auto Programming**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:123
msgid "字段映射完成后，点击 **运行自动编程**："
msgstr "Once field mapping is done, click **Run Auto-Programming**:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:125
msgid "系统结合视觉检测结果和 CAD 坐标，自动匹配每个元件并写入标识 / 封装 / 料号。"
msgstr ""
"The system fuses the vision results with the CAD coordinates, auto-"
"matches each component, and writes designator / package / part number."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:127
msgid "若自动匹配成功，约 30 秒后进入产品编程界面："
msgstr ""
"On successful match, after about 30 seconds the wizard hands off to the "
"product programming page:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "完成自动编程示意"
msgstr "Auto-Programming completion illustration"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "完成自动编程示意（元件列表）"
msgstr "Auto-Programming completion — component list view"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:137
msgid "同类封装的元件会自动分组，方便后续批量调整与训练。更多详情请参见 :ref:`料号封装和分组` 。"
msgstr ""
"Components sharing the same package are grouped automatically so they can"
" be batch-adjusted and trained later; see :ref:`料号封装和分组` for details."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "数据集分组后示意"
msgstr "Dataset after grouping"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:143
msgid "**步骤四（自动对齐失败时）：坐标对齐调整**"
msgstr "**Step 4 (when auto-alignment fails): coordinate alignment**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:145
msgid "若 CAD 坐标与视觉识别结果偏差过大，系统会在匹配失败后自动跳转至 **对齐坐标** 界面："
msgstr ""
"If the CAD coordinates and the vision results diverge too far, the system"
" falls through to the **Align Coordinates** screen after the match fails:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst
msgid "半自动编程坐标对齐失败界面"
msgstr "Semi-Auto Programming coordinate-alignment failure screen"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:151
msgid "在该界面可使用以下工具手动调整对齐："
msgstr "Use the following tools to align manually:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:153
msgid "**平移（X / Y 方向）** — 拖动滑条或输入偏移量。"
msgstr "**Translate (X / Y)** — drag the slider or type an offset."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:154
msgid "**旋转** — 输入角度（度）顺时针或逆时针旋转。"
msgstr ""
"**Rotate** — enter an angle (degrees) to rotate clockwise or counter-"
"clockwise."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:155
msgid "**水平翻转 / 垂直翻转** — 按钮切换镜像方向。"
msgstr "**Flip horizontal / Flip vertical** — buttons that mirror the layout."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:157
msgid ""
"大致对齐后，点击 **重新分析** 重新执行匹配。在 **对齐坐标** 界面也可调整 **CAD 对齐容差 (px)**，或切换 "
"**使用元件模板** / **仅编程 CAD 中的元件** 后再点击 **重新分析**。"
msgstr ""
"After roughly aligning, click **Re-analyze** to rerun the match. On the "
"**Align Coordinates** screen you can also adjust the **CAD alignment "
"tolerance (px)**, or toggle **Use Component Templates** / **Only program "
"components in CAD** before clicking **Re-analyze** again."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:160
msgid ""
"首次运行时已完成的器件检测结果会被缓存。只要拍摄图像未变化，**重新分析** 只重新执行坐标对齐，而不再重复耗时的 AI "
"检测，因此多次手动对齐后的 **重新分析** 通常只需数秒。调整 **CAD 对齐容差 (px)** 或切换上述选项后的 **重新分析** "
"同样命中缓存。"
msgstr ""
"The component detection completed on the first run is cached. As long as "
"the captured image is unchanged, **Re-analyze** only re-runs the "
"coordinate alignment and does not repeat the time-consuming AI detection,"
" so a **Re-analyze** after several manual alignment attempts usually "
"takes only seconds. A **Re-analyze** after adjusting the **CAD alignment "
"tolerance (px)** or toggling the options above also hits the cache."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:162
msgid "**编程后的自动处理：拼板构建与模型训练**"
msgstr "**Post-programming automation: panel building and model training**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:164
msgid ""
"点击 **运行自动编程** "
"后，除生成检测框外，系统还会根据两个相互独立的选项自动完成后续步骤。整个过程中界面保持锁定并显示处理状态（例如\"正在构建拼板阵列…\"），直到全部处理完成，期间无需操作。"
msgstr ""
"After you click **Run auto programming**, the system not only generates "
"the detection boxes but also automatically carries out follow-up steps, "
"governed by two independent options. Throughout the process the screen "
"stays locked and shows a processing status (for example, \"Building panel"
" array…\") until everything is finished; no action is needed in the "
"meantime."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:166
msgid ""
"**自动构建拼板阵列** — 若在自动编程配置的 **拼板** 面板中开启了 **启用拼板** 并填写了大于 1 的 **行数** / "
"**列数**，系统会在编程完成后自动以所绘检测区域注册基准子板、自动检测其余子板位置、并执行自动调整拼板对齐。此过程替代了原本需在 "
":ref:`PCB 拼板` 页手动完成的\"管理子板模板 → 自动检测 → 自动调整拼板\"操作。"
msgstr ""
"**Automatic panel-array building** — if **Enable panelization** is turned"
" on in the **Panelization** panel of the auto-program configuration and "
"**Num of Rows** / **Num of Cols** are greater than 1, then after "
"programming finishes the system automatically registers the base sub-"
"board from the drawn detection region, auto-detects the positions of the "
"remaining sub-boards, and runs auto-adjust to align the array. This "
"replaces the \"Manage Base Panel → Auto-Detect → Auto-Adjust Panel\" "
"steps that previously had to be done by hand on the :ref:`PCB 拼板` page."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:169
msgid ""
"启用拼板时，自动编程检测区域必须绘制在 **单个代表性子板** "
"周围，而非整块拼板。配置界面也会给出同样的提示。系统以该区域作为单个子板的模板来检测其余子板；若框选整块拼板，将只能检测出一个子板。"
msgstr ""
"When panelization is enabled, the auto-program detection region must be "
"drawn around **a single representative sub-board**, not the whole panel. "
"The configuration screen gives the same reminder. The system uses that "
"region as the template for a single sub-board to detect the others; if "
"you frame the whole panel, only one sub-board can be detected."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:171
msgid ""
"若自动检测在尝试次数内未能匹配设定的行 × 列，系统会弹出警告，产品保留为 **单板** 而不注册拼板，随后仍按 **自动训练** "
"设置继续。此时可在 :ref:`PCB 拼板` 页手动完成拼板。"
msgstr ""
"If automatic detection cannot match the configured rows × cols within the"
" trial limit, the system shows a warning, keeps the product as a **single"
" board** without registering a panel array, and then continues according "
"to the **Auto-train after programming** setting. You can then panelize "
"manually on the :ref:`PCB 拼板` page."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:173
msgid ""
"**自动训练模型** — 由 **运行自动编程** 按钮旁的 **自动训练** "
"复选框控制（默认勾选，选择会被记住）。勾选后，编程及拼板完成后系统自动依次执行模型训练、检测参数生成与重新评估，无需手动触发；取消勾选则跳过训练，可稍后在产品编程界面手动训练。该选项与拼板相互独立——无论是否拼板，勾选即训练。"
msgstr ""
"**Automatic model training** — controlled by the **Auto-train after "
"programming** checkbox next to the **Run auto programming** button "
"(checked by default; the choice is remembered). When checked, once "
"programming (and panel building) finish the system automatically runs "
"model training, detection-parameter generation, and re-evaluation in "
"turn, with no manual trigger; when unchecked it skips training, which you"
" can run later by hand on the product-programming page. This option is "
"independent of panelization — checked means train, whether or not the "
"product is panelized."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:-1
msgid "自动编程配置的拼板面板：启用拼板、行数 / 列数输入，及单个代表性子板提示"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:-1
msgid "添加CAD步骤中\"运行自动编程\"按钮旁的\"自动训练\"复选框"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:184
msgid "**常见问题与排查**"
msgstr "**Common questions and troubleshooting**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:186
msgid "**CAD 导入后自动对齐失败**：进入坐标对齐界面，使用平移、旋转、翻转工具大致对齐后，点击 **重新分析** 即可。"
msgstr ""
"**Auto-alignment fails after CAD import**: open the coordinate-alignment "
"screen, roughly align with Translate / Rotate / Flip, then click **Re-"
"analyze**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:187
msgid "**坐标点位错乱无法对齐**：检查坐标单位（mil ↔ mm），确认选择与 CAD 文件一致。"
msgstr ""
"**Coordinates won't line up at all**: check the coordinate unit (mil ↔ "
"mm) matches the CAD file."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:188
msgid "**全自动漏检少量极小器件**：手动补录并训练，或优化光照 / 清晰度后再次运行自动编程。"
msgstr ""
"**Full Auto-Programming misses a few very small components**: add them "
"manually and retrain, or improve lighting / sharpness and rerun Auto-"
"Programming."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:189
msgid ""
"**文件上传失败 / 乱码**：当前不支持 ``.xls`` 文件，需转换为 ``.csv``\\ （UTF-8 编码）。使用 Excel "
"另存时请选择 **CSV UTF-8（逗号分隔）** 格式，不要选普通 CSV。"
msgstr ""
"**Upload fails / garbled characters**: ``.xls`` is not supported — "
"convert to ``.csv`` (UTF-8). When saving from Excel, pick **CSV UTF-8 "
"(Comma delimited)**, not the regular CSV format."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:190
msgid "**特殊字符（如 ± 符号）解析失败**：将文件中的非标准字符替换为标准 ASCII 字符（例如 ``±`` → ``+/-``）后重试。"
msgstr ""
"**Special characters (e.g. ±) fail to parse**: replace non-standard "
"characters with plain ASCII (for example ``±`` → ``+/-``) and retry."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:191
msgid "**CAD 自动编程时小区域元件漏识别**：自动编程完成后请手动检查并补录漏识别的元件。可考虑下次提供更完整的 CAD 文件以缩小自动识别范围。"
msgstr ""
"**Small-area components missed during CAD Auto-Programming**: review and "
"add missing components manually after the run. For next time, consider "
"supplying a more complete CAD file to narrow the auto-detection scope."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/auto_programming.rst:192
msgid ""
"**拼板自动检测失败**：自动编程时若提示自动拼板检测未匹配设定的行 × "
"列，产品会保留为单板。请确认检测区域仅框选了单个代表性子板（而非整块拼板）后重试；仍失败时可在 :ref:`PCB 拼板` 页手动拼板。"
msgstr ""
"**Automatic panel detection failed**: if, during auto-programming, you "
"are told that automatic panel detection did not match the configured rows"
" × cols, the product is kept as a single board. Confirm that the "
"detection region frames only a single representative sub-board (not the "
"whole panel) and retry; if it still fails, you can panelize manually on "
"the :ref:`PCB 拼板` page."

